  "summary": "MoinMoin Insertion of Sensitive Information into Log File",
  "details": "An information leak was discovered in MoinMoin's debug reporting version 1.5.7, which could expose information about the versions of software running on the host system.  MoinMoin administrators can add \"show_traceback=0\" to their site configurations to disable debug tracebacks.",
